  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657480/extras/c28674a1d9419cd9bb8e9c5ffc4c7147.poster.avif?t=1728952415\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657480/extras/c28674a1d9419cd9bb8e9c5ffc4c7147.webm?t=1728952415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657480/extras/c28674a1d9419cd9bb8e9c5ffc4c7147.mp4?t=1728952415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Everybody has hit someone with a bat or a ball at least once.<br><br>Experience the action-packed evolution of the world's greatest sport through multiple eras of history, from its humble prehistoric beginnings to taking its rightful place among the stars.<br><br>Cricket Through the Ages is the factual, physics-based chronicle of humanity's passion for the spirit of cricket. Whether solo or with an able partner, batter up for a cricket-based game that's anything but cricket.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657480/extras/4d1ce17d64427e6e99aa47fcbe294f03.poster.avif?t=1728952415\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657480/extras/4d1ce17d64427e6e99aa47fcbe294f03.webm?t=1728952415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657480/extras/4d1ce17d64427e6e99aa47fcbe294f03.mp4?t=1728952415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Master the ancient art of cricket through the miracle of a simple, one button control scheme.<br></li><li>Play through nine unique, historically accurate game modes solo or against a friendly rival.<br></li><li>Physics-based buffoonery from the creators of Broforce and Genital Jousting.</li></ul>",
